                                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Windows 11's Paint, Snipping Tool, and Notepad Apps Are About to Get New Features]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/windows-11-paint-snipping-tool-notepad-apps-new-features/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Arol Wright]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/windows-11-logo.jpg" length="106" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Windows]]></category><category><![CDATA[Windows 11]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Triple update, triple fun.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>It’s always a good day when Windows’ default apps get updates. Brand-new versions of apps like Paint, Snipping Tool, and Notepad are coming, and they have a healthy amount of new features you need to check out.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Thu, 18 Sep 2025 11:36:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/windows-11-paint-snipping-tool-notepad-apps-new-features/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[12 macOS Tahoe Settings to Change Right Away]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/macos-26-tahoe-settings-to-change-right-away/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Tim Brookes]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/macos-26-appearance-toggles.jpg" length="789" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Mac]]></category><category><![CDATA[macOS]]></category><category><![CDATA[Privacy]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[customization]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            From themes and Liquid Glass to Spotlight and Control Center.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Apple has finally unleashed a brand new version of macOS, with a standardized version number and a fresh, glassy look. In addition to the obvious differences, macOS 26 Tahoe has a few extra settings you might want to tweak compared to the previous release.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Thu, 18 Sep 2025 11:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/macos-26-tahoe-settings-to-change-right-away/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[I Leaned on the Amazfit Balance 2 for All Things Health and Wellness — Here’s How It Did]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/amazfit-balance-2-review/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Michael Bizzaco]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2025/09/amazfit-balance-2-hero-1.jpeg" length="425" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Android]]></category><category><![CDATA[Wearables]]></category><category><![CDATA[Amazfit Balance 2]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Three cheers for the wearable underdog. 
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Amazfit-Balance-Sapphire-Display-Offline-Battery/dp/B0F9JFCYNX?tag=hotoge-20&ascsubtag=UUhtgUeUpU2016537&asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtogeek.com%2Famazfit-balance-2-review%2F&asc_campaign=Authority" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" class="norewrite noskim">Amazfit Balance 2</a> is proof that third-party wearables can be just as impressive as the mainline competition. This fitness watch delivers remarkable battery life, smooth-running software, and more health and wellness features than you’ll know what to do with. It also looks fantastic and is comfortable to wear.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Thu, 18 Sep 2025 10:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/amazfit-balance-2-review/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Toyota, Lexus, and Subaru Issue Repair Recall—Here’s What to Know]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/toyota-lexus-subaru-issue-repair-recall/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Adam Gray]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025_toyota_tacoma_trdoffroad_bronzeoxide_001.jpg" length="450" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Automotive]]></category><category><![CDATA[Electric Vehicles]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Toyota, Lexus and Subaru EVs face fresh recalls over heating system flaws, extending a wave of recent safety notices for the automakers.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p><a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/lexus-models-you-should-buy-used/" target="_blank">Lexus</a>, <a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/tag/toyota/" target="_blank">Toyota</a>, and <a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/2025-subaru-forester-most-versatile-model-yet/" target="_blank">Subaru</a> drivers are facing not one but two new recalls that could impact whether their cars are safe to drive.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Thu, 18 Sep 2025 09:25:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/toyota-lexus-subaru-issue-repair-recall/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[You Home Screen Is Getting in “Shape” With the Latest Android 16 Beta]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/android-16-qpr2-beta-2-icon-shapes/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Joe Fedewa]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/android-16-hero.jpg" length="68" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Android]]></category><category><![CDATA[Android Phones & Tablets]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google Pixel]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            A fresh look for your Android home screen is on the horizon...
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Android 16 has been officially available for <a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/android-16-june-pixel-drop-official/" target="_blank">a few months now</a>, but the beta program is still going strong. The second beta for the upcoming quarterly release (QPR2) has just been released for Pixel phones, and it has some cool goodies.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 21:12:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/android-16-qpr2-beta-2-icon-shapes/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Google Is Switching Up Its Discover Feed]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/google-is-switching-up-its-discover-feed/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Arol Wright]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/illustration-of-google-search-results-cluttered-with-icons-like-trash-bins-thumbs-down-and-warning-signs-with-a-cracked-google-logo-above-the-search-bar.png" length="535" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Web]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            You might find it to be a lot worse.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Your Discover feed always gives you a healthy feed of news and articles—you might've even reached this very post through Discover. Now, though, it's about to get a lot worse.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 20:31:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/google-is-switching-up-its-discover-feed/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Grounded Sci-Fi—8 Mind-Bending Movies That Never Leave Earth]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/grounded-sci-fi-mind-bending-movies-that-never-leave-earth/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Faisal Rasool]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/collage-featuring-scenes-from-source-code-district-9-and-in-time.png" length="3098" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Streaming]]></category><category><![CDATA[ Movies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Streaming]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Take a break from spaceship battles and enjoy some science fiction on terra firma.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p><a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/classic-sci-fi-movies-that-were-inspired-by-star-trek/" target="_blank">Sci-fi movies</a> are typically saturated with aliens, space travel, distant galaxies, and other mind-bending science fiction.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 20:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/grounded-sci-fi-mind-bending-movies-that-never-leave-earth/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Get a Retractable USB-C Charger for $10]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/get-a-retractable-usb-c-charger-for-10/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jorge A. Aguilar]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/the-lisen-retractable-usb-c-charger-with-its-cord-being-pulled-out-for-a-user.jpg" length="299" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Android]]></category><category><![CDATA[Phone charger]]></category><category><![CDATA[Deals]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            It's hard to say no when a deal is over half off.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Right now, you can get a Lisen retractable USB-C charger for just <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DGTG9G5F?tag=hotoge-20&ascsubtag=UUhtgUeUpU2016649&asc_refurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.howtogeek.com%2Fget-a-retractable-usb-c-charger-for-10%2F&asc_campaign=Affiliate" target="_blank" class="norewrite noskim" rel="sponsored nofollow">$10 on Amazon</a>. This is a massive 50% discount off the usual $28 price. You can also save an extra $4.20 with the on-page coupon, making this a shockingly low price for a 45W charger that eliminates cable clutter.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 19:14:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/get-a-retractable-usb-c-charger-for-10/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[This Could Be the Most Underrated Car Brand in North America Right Now]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/could-this-be-the-most-underrated-car-brand-in-north-america-righ/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Brent vd Schyff]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/92_nsx_03-1200x784.jpg" length="112" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Automotive]]></category><category><![CDATA[Honda]]></category><category><![CDATA[Toyota]]></category><category><![CDATA[Accord]]></category><category><![CDATA[Camry]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Discover why Honda, a consistent performer in the automotive industry, is often overlooked despite its impressive achievements and cult-like following
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Marketing plays a role in the modern game, pushing a narrative and getting in your face more than others. The same spending on the budget might not be possible from every manufacturer out there. <a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/best-all-around-family-sedan-2025/" target="_blank">One particular car brand</a> doesn't occupy as much limelight but, however, still continues to deliver rock-solid cars, impressing both those who write about them and those who buy and enjoy them. That brand is Honda.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 19:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/could-this-be-the-most-underrated-car-brand-in-north-america-righ/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Vivaldi Web Browser Is Getting More Customizable Tabs]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/vivaldi-update-lets-you-switch-tab-locations/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jorge A. Aguilar]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/the-vivaldi-browser-with-the-tabs-being-pulled-out-as-if-they-can-be-moved.jpg" length="142" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Web]]></category><category><![CDATA[web browsers]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            You can move your tabs to the left, right, top, and bottom.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Vivaldi just released version 7.6 of its web browser. While a lot of other browsers are pushing one-size-fits-all interfaces and templates, Vivaldi is letting you decide how your browser looks and where your tabs go.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Wed, 17 Sep 2025 18:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/vivaldi-update-lets-you-switch-tab-locations/</guid></item></channel>
